    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Macro Browser作为核心系统。那用户这边怎么体现？是一个普通的人形角色吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用一个Person表示用户，描述写成\"A person using Macro Browser\"，强调这是实际使用浏览器的人。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，用户节点已添加。现在画从用户到Macro Browser的关系，标注\"Uses\"，表示使用关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "macroBrowser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要体现Macro Browser的两大能力：传统网页浏览和Web3交互。先做传统这边，有个外部系统叫\"Web Content\"，代表常规网站和应用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "webSites"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Web Content外部系统。关系线画从Macro Browser指向它，标注\"Accesses\"，表示浏览器访问这些网站内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "macroBrowser",
        "webSites"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Web3这边需要三个外部系统。首先是DApps，去中心化应用，描述要强调\"running on blockchains\"。",
